PrecisReappointment of JOE OHOKANNOAK, of Cambridge Bay, Northwest Territories, WILLIAM LYALL, of Cambridge Bay, Northwest Territories, DAVID ALAGALAK, of Arviat, Northwest Territories, MEEKA KILABUK, of Iqaluit, Northwest Territories, and CLARA O'GORMAN, of Cambridge Bay, Northwest Territories, as members of the Nunavut Implementation Commission, to hold office during pleasure, for a term ending June 30, 1999, effective December 10, 1998.
